OL,3,CTom Davies opens up on mental health
OL,4,Cstruggles during injury layoff
OL,6,FSheffield United footballer Tom Davies
OL,7,Fhas opened up about his mental health
OL,8,Fstruggles after missing much of last
OL,9,Fseason through injury.
OL,11,FTom Davies, 26, has spent more time on
OL,12,Fthe sidelines than playing for the
OL,13,FBlades since signing for them at the
OL,14,Fstart of the 2023-24 season due to a
OL,15,Fhamstring injury.
OL,17,FThe midfielder said spending several
OL,18,Fmonths in rehabilitation had a
OL,19,Fdetrimental effect on his mental
OL,20,Fhealth.
