OL,3,CTom Davies opens up on mental health
OL,4,Cstruggles during injury layoff
OL,6,FDavies, who joined United from
OL,7,Fhometown club Everton, said: "Football
OL,8,Fis the only thing and the most
OL,9,Fimportant thing, which it has been for
OL,10,Fme for a long time. But when it was
OL,11,Fthe only thing in my life and it
OL,12,Fwasn't going well, it was like my
OL,13,Fwhole world wasn't going well.
OL,15,F"Being a man involved in football,
OL,16,Fbeing a Northern man from a working-
OL,17,Fclass family, it can be that you just
OL,18,Fwork hard and you get on with things.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
