OL,3,CTom Davies opens up on mental health
OL,4,Cstruggles during injury layoff
OL,6,F"You just try your best and things
OL,7,Fwill come good, and you don't really
OL,8,Fconcern yourself with the other stuff."
OL,10,FDavies played just nine times last
OL,11,Fseason before travelling to Germany to
OL,12,Fsee a specialist in the summer.
OL,14,FHe shared advice for people struggling
OL,15,Fwith their mental health who may be
OL,16,Ftoo scared to speak up.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
