OL,3,CTom Davies opens up on mental health
OL,4,Cstruggles during injury layoff
OL,6,F"The thing I realise now on the other
OL,7,Fside of actually sharing and speaking
OL,8,Fup is it's so much more freeing,
OL,9,Frather than holding onto these
OL,10,Femotions and trying to deal with
OL,11,Feverything by yourself," he said.
OL,13,F"Just to let them go and become more
OL,14,Ffree in that way, it can age your life
OL,15,Fin a whole different way."
OL,17,FSince breaking through at boyhood club
OL,18,FEverton, Davies has always been known
OL,19,Ffor his signature long blonde hair.
