OL,3,CTom Davies opens up on mental health
OL,4,Cstruggles during injury layoff
OL,6,FBut last year he shaved it off to
OL,7,Fraise awareness for mental health
OL,8,Fcharities.
OL,10,F"I wanted a haircut, it was time for a
OL,11,Fchange for me. I'm very lucky to play
OL,12,Ffootball and I'm very lucky I have
OL,13,Fthis platform where I can speak to
OL,14,Fpeople like yourself", he said.
OL,16,F"I try and speak up as much a I can on
OL,17,Fmy Instagram and whenever I get a
OL,18,Fchance like this I do like to speak
OL,19,Fabout it because I have this
OL,20,Fopportunity and I want to use it for
OL,21,Fsome good."
