OL,3,CTom Davies opens up on mental health
OL,4,Cstruggles during injury layoff
OL,6,FDuring his time on the sidelines,
OL,7,FDavies opened a sustainable business
OL,8,Fthat turns used chopsticks into
OL,9,Ffurniture.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's been a really healthy
OL,12,Fdistraction for me because even though
OL,13,Ffootball has probably felt like its
OL,14,Fbeen a big stagnant, that's really
OL,15,Fgrown.
OL,17,F"Taking this journey myself, I can
OL,18,Fthen learn stuff through my day to day
OL,19,Flife and try and understand what I
OL,20,Fneed to do more of, and I just want to
OL,21,Ftry and do some good in the world."
